OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dull wet start. Brightening
OL,6,Fsomewhat during the morning but
OL,7,Ffurther heavy showers soon pushing in,
OL,8,Fperhaps with thunder. Some brief sunny
OL,9,Fintervals too. Moderate southwesterly
OL,10,Fbreeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining mostly cloudy this
OL,13,Fevening and tonight with frequent
OL,14,Fshowers, some heavy, and a few drier
OL,15,Fclearer intervals. Freshening
OL,16,Fnorthwesterly winds by morning.
OL,17,
OL,18,CThursday:FRather cloudy with rain or
OL,19,Fshowers, some turning heavy at times.
OL,20,FModerate to fresh west to northwest
OL,21,Fbreeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
