OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBrighter
OL,6,Fwith sunny intervals and a few showers
OL,7,Fon Friday. Rain on Saturday, some
OL,8,Fheavy, brightening later. Then back to
OL,9,Fsunshine and showers on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
